    <p class="section-number">04 · Honest scope</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">What we do for rack conveyor, and what we don't.</h2>

    <p><strong>We service:</strong> Hobart CRS, Champion 86, Jackson AJ, Insinger, Stero, two-tank and three-tank rack conveyor configurations, electric and steam-injected tank heaters, NSF 180°F booster compliance verification, conveyor drive systems, door and curtain interlocks, drain systems, wash arms.</p>

    <p><strong>We don't do:</strong> new rack conveyor installation (specialty installer trade through manufacturer dealer network); steam line or steam boiler service (separate plumbing trade); chemical dispenser supply contracts (Ecolab, Auto-Chlor, Diversey, separate service track); ventilation hood work above the dishwasher (see <a href="/commercial/exhaust-hood-repair/">commercial exhaust hood repair</a>).</p>
