    <h2 class="section-title">Five rack conveyor platforms cover most of LA.</h2>

    <p><strong>Hobart</strong> (ITW Food Equipment Group): CRS-66A, CRS-86A. The most-deployed platform in LA restaurants. We carry common parts. See <a href="/brands/hobart-dishwasher-repair/">Hobart commercial dishwasher repair</a>.</p>

    <p><strong>Champion</strong> (Ali Group, sister brand to Scotsman ice machines and Beverage-Air refrigeration): 86 series. Mid-premium, common in chains. See <a href="/brands/champion-dishwasher-repair/">Champion commercial dishwasher repair</a>.</p>

    <p><strong>Jackson</strong> (Hoshizaki America acquired): AJ-66, AJ-80. Strong post-acquisition parts availability. See <a href="/brands/jackson-dishwasher-repair/">Jackson commercial dishwasher repair</a>.</p>

    <p><strong>Insinger and Stero</strong>: less common but still serviced. Insinger known for stainless build quality, Stero for institutional-scale rack conveyors.</p>
