    <p class="section-number">07 · Why operators call us</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Eight reasons.</h2>

    <ul class="why-list">
      <li><strong>Rack conveyor specialization.</strong> Hobart CRS, Champion 86, Jackson AJ. Different drive geometries, different chain pitches, different sprocket counts. We identify by serial number first.</li>
      <li><strong>NSF 180°F final rinse documentation.</strong> We measure at the manifold during a live cycle and document for health-code records (LADPH, OC Health Care Agency, Ventura County Environmental Health).</li>
      <li><strong>Conveyor drive system as a unit.</strong> Past year 7, we replace chain plus sprocket plus motor as a related system rather than chasing one component at a time.</li>
      <li><strong>BHGS #A49573 plus EPA 608 Universal #1346255700410.</strong> Verifiable. Required for any commercial appliance work in California.</li>
      <li><strong>24/7 phone answering, no emergency surcharge.</strong> $120 anytime.</li>
      <li><strong>Same-day across LA, OC, Ventura.</strong> Eight branches.</li>
      <li><strong>Common parts on the van.</strong> Conveyor motors, drive chains, booster heater elements, door switches.</li>
      <li><strong>Honest replace-vs-repair</strong> on year 12+ machines. Sometimes the math says replace. We say so.</li>
    </ul>

    <p>Sister sub-services: <a href="/commercial/dishwasher-repair/flight-type-dishwasher-repair/">flight type</a>, <a href="/commercial/dishwasher-repair/undercounter-dishwasher-repair/">undercounter</a>, <a href="/commercial/dishwasher-repair/glass-washer-repair/">glass washer</a>. Parent: <a href="/commercial/dishwasher-repair/">commercial dishwasher repair</a>. Credentials: <a href="/credentials/licensed/">BHGS license</a>, <a href="/credentials/epa-certified/">EPA 608</a>.</p>
  </div>
